=== Social Connection Strategies

Social isolation compounds the impact of severe illness. Strategies to maintain peer connection:

    - *Low-demand communication*: Text messaging, voice messages allow asynchronous connection
    - *Brief video calls*: 5–15 minute video calls with friends during good periods
    - *Online communities*: Age-appropriate online groups for chronic illness (finding peers who understand)
    - *Creative projects*: Collaborative online projects with friends (writing, gaming, art)
    - *Card/letter exchange*: Receiving mail from friends; dictating responses if writing impossible

